Automated Blocklist & Firewall Sync

Often after TI lookup, IOCs must be blocked across multiple tools (EDR, NGFW, proxy). XSOAR automates cross-platform updates.

### Flow (ASCII Diagram)

+--------------------------+
| Malicious IOC Confirmed  |
+--------------------------+
            |
            v
+--------------------------+
| XSOAR Playbook Trigger   |
| (IOC = "High Risk")      |
+--------------------------+
            |
            v
+--------------------------+
| Push to Firewall (PAN-OS)|
+--------------------------+
            |
            v
+--------------------------+
| Push to EDR (CrowdStrike)|
+--------------------------+
            |
            v
+--------------------------+
| Push to Proxy/SWG        |
+--------------------------+
            |
            v
+--------------------------+
| Confirm in SIEM Logs     |
+--------------------------+

**Benefit:** single IOC decision â†’ automatic multi-tool enforcement in under 1 minute.
